  "name": "Captains Fish and Chicken",
  "description": "Walk into Captains Fish and Chicken on 1st Ave NE and you smell it immediately — that unmistakable aroma of hand-breaded catfish sizzling in the fryer. We don't do frozen fillets. We don't do shortcuts. Every piece of fish, every chicken wing, every hush puppy gets fried to order. Hot. Crispy. Done right.\n\nWe're a family-owned spot in Cedar Rapids, IA, serving portions big enough to satisfy a lumberjack and prices gentle enough for a lunch break. Most combos run $10–$15 with fries and bread included. Our regulars? They come back for the crunch. That golden crust that crackles when you bite into it. The juicy meat inside. The seasoning that hits every taste bud.\n\nWhether you're dining in at our clean, welcoming spot on 1st Ave or ordering through UberEats and DoorDash for delivery, you get the same quality — fried fresh, never sitting under a heat lamp. That's the Captain's way.",
